From a555302a27e41bdcdf2a7b8be70465977ef48228 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: mpl_risk <dev@example.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 22:06:00 -1000
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] build: exclude examples/ from the library tsc build

The exclude entry still names example-app/, a directory that was renamed to
examples/. ts-loader therefore type-checks the React example apps as part of
the library build and fails with 59 TS17004 errors ('Cannot use JSX unless the
--jsx flag is provided'), so `npm run build` does not succeed on a clean
checkout.
---
 tsconfig.json | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/tsconfig.json b/tsconfig.json
index b85e14d..e2efe6b 100644
--- a/tsconfig.json
+++ b/tsconfig.json
@@ -15,6 +15,7 @@
     "skipLibCheck": true
   },
   "exclude": [
-    "example-app",
+    "examples",
+    "node_modules"
   ]
 }
\ No newline at end of file
